	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings Vladin,<br><br>The Shiny Brass Shield (SBS) is not a quest item, but a semi-rare drop item from the Orc Trainer in Crushbone.  The Trainer spawns up on the Hill just to the right once you enter the courtyard in Crushbone.  He will spawn right in the center of the platform, along with several other Orcs. It is a great place for XP at level 12 and Crushbone is a great zone...that's why it's so crowded! The Trainer does not drop the SBS everytime.<br><br>Ghoulbane is a nice weapon well into your 40's but eventually other weapons begin to outdamage it, even against undead.<br><br>Good luck with the SBS.<br><br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>49th Circle of Dwarven Paladins<br>Twilight Brethren<br><br>"Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness"<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
